data.description: Welcome to this stunning home located in the desirable Waterstone subdivision! With five bedrooms and three  bathrooms, this spacious and upgraded residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. Step inside and be  greeted by the beautiful upgrades that adorn this home. The brand-new AC upstairs ensures optimal climate control  throughout the year. A new deck provides the perfect outdoor space for entertaining or simply enjoying a peaceful  evening. The kitchen boasts new appliances, including a dual air fryer in the stove, making meal preparation a breeze.  Fresh interior paint adds a modern touch, while the updated kitchen with granite countertops is a chef's dream. The  metal stair pickets lend a contemporary feel to the interior, and the new barn doors and enlarged pantry add both  functionality and charm. New light fixtures and interior hardware complete the elegant look of this home. In addition to these upgrades, this home also features a full unfinished basement, offering  endless possibilities for customization and expansion. The fenced backyard provides privacy and  a safe space for outdoor activities with a screened-in porch. Cozy up on chilly evenings by the  wood-burning fireplace in the living room, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The guest  bedroom on the main floor, complete with a full bath, offers convenience and comfort for  overnight guests. The master bedroom on the main level boasts his and her sinks and a large  walk-in closet, providing ample storage space. Located in the desirable Waterstone subdivision,  this home offers a fantastic opportunity to own a move-in-ready property with numerous  upgrades and amenities. Don't miss out on the chance to make this your dream home!
